name: wp_uniqip v0.0.1_alpha:
description: wordpress plugin to display number of unique site visits per day
language: python
interpreter: python 2.6.5

HOWTO:

1) edit /etc/apache2/vhosts.d/DOMAIN.NAME and add this lines:
    LogFormat "%h %l %u %t \"%r\" %>s %b" common
    CustomLog /var/log/apache2/domain.name_log common
2) edit line number 56 to real path of your apache log file
3) echo "0 0 * * * root /bin/sh rotate.sh" >> /etc/crontab
4) echo "2-59/5 * * * * user parser.py" >> /etc/crontab
5) cp UniqIP.php /var/www/data/domain.name/wp-content/plugins/UniqIP/
6) cp mysql.inc /var/www/data/domain.name/wp-content/plugins/UniqIP/
7) http://domain.name/wp-admin/plugins.php
    "UniqIP Activate"

That's all
